'''''The Statesman''''' is the oldest newspaper at [[Stony Brook University]], a flagship university of the SUNY ([[State University of New York]]) system. It was founded in 1957 as the Sucolian at the State University Campus On Long Island at [[Oyster Bay (hamlet), New York|Oyster Bay]], the precursor to Stony Brook University.

